      "uuid": "80291cd1-b68a-4dd6-a31b-effab5aeef0f",
      "text": " This particular listing shows \"N/A\" for the fuel economy/gas mileage. However, I can tell you that the 2005 Chevrolet Express 2500 with the 6.0L V8 engine typically gets approximately:\n\n- 11-13 MPG in the city\n- 14-16 MPG on the highway\n- 12-14 MPG combined\n\nKeep in mind these are approximate figures and actual fuel economy can vary based on:\n- Driving conditions\n- Cargo weight\n- Driving style\n- Vehicle maintenance\n- Whether it's been modified\n\nGiven that this is a work van with over 111,000 miles, the actual fuel economy might be slightly lower than these estimates.",
      "sender": "assistant",
      "index": 1,
      "created_at": "2024-10-21T23:34:04.072391Z",
      "updated_at": "2024-10-21T23:34:04.072391Z",
