      "uuid": "23fb2e8b-6361-47ec-99cc-bca44512afef",
      "text": " Looking at these Chevy Express 2500 vans, I'll help you compare them:\n\n2005 Express 2500\n- $7,998\n- 111,640 miles (lowest)\n- 6.0L V8 engine\n- Unknown history\n\n2006 Express 2500\n- $7,995 ($930 below market)\n- 161,057 miles\n- 8cyl engine\n- 3 owners, personal use\n- No accidents\n\n2008 Express 2500\n- $7,950 ($3,232 below market)\n- 153,600 miles\n- 8cyl engine\n- 2 owners, personal use\n- No accidents\n\nBest value appears to be the 2008 model because:\n- Newest year\n- Significantly below market price\n- Clean history with only 2 owners\n- Mid-range mileage\n- Only 2 miles away from your location\n\nHowever, if lowest mileage is your priority, the 2005 model has about 40-50k fewer miles than the others. But we don't have accident/owner history on that one.\n\nAll these will have similar fuel economy since they're all 2500 series with V8 engines - expect around:\n- 12-14 MPG city\n- 16-17 MPG highway\n- Worse when loaded or towing\n\nWould you like me to analyze any other aspects of these vans?",
      "sender": "assistant",
      "index": 11,
      "created_at": "2024-10-21T23:57:42.315198Z",
      "updated_at": "2024-10-21T23:57:42.315198Z",
