      "uuid": "a8808907-caba-426a-86d5-a84c30712c7f",
      "text": " The 2008 Chevrolet Express 2500 is at Western Motors, which is 2 miles away according to the listing.\n\nThe dealership locations for all three vans are:\n- 2008 Express: Western Motors (2 miles away)\n- 2006 Express: Elegant Auto Sales (10 miles away)\n- 2005 Express: Rocket Car Company ((626) area code suggests Los Angeles area)\n\nSince the 2008 model is the closest at just 2 miles away, that adds another advantage to its value proposition, as you'll spend less time and fuel getting there to see it.",
      "sender": "assistant",
      "index": 15,
      "created_at": "2024-10-22T00:04:49.257841Z",
